subprogram grants agro to whoever does the highest amount of damage.  There is no reason to put in extra lines of code inorder to say you need a certan amount more damage to get the argo.  <br>There is also a subprogram that caluclates the amount of damage you do.  Str is one factor in this program.  All else being equil the higher your str the more damage you do.  <br>Both the math and the logic of computer programing suggest that Str, and Skill lvl cap do make a differance.  Furthermore this is supported by actual in game results.    </p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
